.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

5 different games are played: chess, whist, scrabble, bridge, poker
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, marigold, tulip, daisy
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, action, time-travel, epic, adventure
1. the british is the person playing scrabble
2. the swedish is the person watching time-travel movies
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing bridge
5. the person playing whist is the person drinking coffee
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching action movies
7. the person playing poker is the person who growsrose
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies
11. the person watching adventures movies is on the left or right of the person who growsrose
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the person who growstulip
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person playing chess
15. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Game		|    poker	|     chess	|      scrabble	|     whist	|     bridge	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Movie-Genre		|     zombie	|    adventure	|     action	|     epic	|      time-travel	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Flower		|   rose	|    daisy	|  marigold	|    tulip	|   balloon-flower	|
